| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1758 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 94aff599-82fe-51e5-af5e-53cfca929ffa"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
